firstly we installed the  neceserry library 
then collect the data with webcam 
then in labelling app we labelled th image to install and run https://github.com/HumanSignal/labelImg 
here detect algoritm should be  yolo and save to labels file in the data folder
and you should write dataset.yaml
and we are ready to train ,execute this command 'python train.py --img 320 --batch 16 --epochs 500 --data dataset.yml --weights yolov5s.pt --workers 2'
and load the model and predict 